      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) holds ISO 9001 certification; FDA-internal solver instance under configuration management with version-controlled input decks.",
      "rationale": "All three modeling teams used commercially validated FEA codes under documented QMS procedures. Ansys 2022 R2 release notes and regression test suite reviewed. Achieved level meets required level."
