      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 is the accepted FDA standard for pedicle screw construct mechanical testing. The validation scenario replicates the exact test geometry, loading mode, and acceptance criteria used in the regulatory submission. High relevance of validation activity to COU confirmed. Achieved level 3."
